1
00:00:15,140 --> 00:00:25,160


2
00:00:25,160 --> 00:00:30,359
♫  Happily tossing and turning in the spring and autumn  ♫

3
00:00:30,359 --> 00:00:34,980
♫  Nothing but love and freedom  ♫

4
00:00:34,980 --> 00:00:41,099
♫  Over thorny roads, across treacherous heights  ♫

5
00:00:41,099 --> 00:00:47,879
♫  After a thousand sails have passed, who will swim with you  ♫

6
00:00:47,879 --> 00:00:53,159
♫  I'm willing to go through the ups and downs of the world for the sake of the people  ♫

7
00:00:53,159 --> 00:00:58,259
♫  Still embracing the original innocence  ♫

8
00:00:58,259 --> 00:01:03,479
♫  The sound of vows falling to the ground, 
 this heart can be proved by Heaven and Earth  ♫

9
00:01:03,479 --> 00:01:08,579
♫  The darker it is the more dazzling like stars there are  ♫

10
00:01:08,580 --> 00:01:13,579
♫  I wish to stride through the ups and downs of fate, and live towards the sun  ♫

11
00:01:13,579 --> 00:01:18,639
♫  Moments turn into eternity, fleeting years become forever  ♫

12
00:01:18,639 --> 00:01:24,000
♫  The road ahead is long, 
 and there is an unquenchable light in my heart  ♫

13
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:29,139
♫  Because someone is waiting for me  ♫

14
00:01:29,139 --> 00:01:36,918
♫  There is one person who will complete the dream  ♫

15
00:01:36,919 --> 00:01:39,119
   

16
00:01:39,119 --> 00:01:43,059
   

17
00:01:43,059 --> 00:01:44,939
   

18
00:01:44,940 --> 00:01:47,940
   

19
00:01:50,910 --> 00:01:54,010
My Lord, the food at your residence is delicious.

20
00:02:00,670 --> 00:02:02,850
My Lord, why aren't you eating?

21
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:06,520
I have eaten at the Ministry of Rites.

22
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:10,780
The communal meal there can't taste better than the food at home.

23
00:02:11,990 --> 00:02:15,960
My Lord, you know my background.

24
00:02:16,500 --> 00:02:21,680
My last name is Mu, but I am not considered part of the Mu family.

25
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:26,240
In that family, no one cares about me.

26
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:29,250
I don't care about them either.

27
00:02:29,250 --> 00:02:32,420
Juli is the only family I have.

28
00:02:36,170 --> 00:02:38,870
You're good at reading the room.

29
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:42,610
If you wished to please your father and his wife,

30
00:02:42,610 --> 00:02:45,890
I'm sure your life at home wouldn't be so tough.

31
00:02:46,940 --> 00:02:49,309
My Lord, you were born into the imperial family.

32
00:02:49,310 --> 00:02:51,530
Don't you get it?

33
00:02:51,530 --> 00:02:55,700
Being liked by someone superior may not necessarily be a good thing.

34
00:02:55,700 --> 00:02:58,560
If I were liked by my father,

35
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:02,190
I would be ostracized and envied by my stepmothers and sisters.

36
00:03:02,190 --> 00:03:06,169
But if I were liked by my stepmothers and sisters, they would pester me.

37
00:03:06,169 --> 00:03:10,480
I wouldn't be able to get any moments of peace to properly study.

38
00:03:11,170 --> 00:03:16,540
To be liked by irrelevant people is meaningless to me.

39
00:03:22,490 --> 00:03:24,190
My Lord,

40
00:03:24,190 --> 00:03:27,790
did I say something wrong?

41
00:03:29,370 --> 00:03:32,060
What about me taking a liking to you?

42
00:03:32,060 --> 00:03:34,840
Am I irrelevant?

43
00:03:37,380 --> 00:03:40,589
My Lord, you are sensible.

44
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:43,160
Stop making fun of me.

45
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,910
Liar.

46
00:03:49,030 --> 00:03:51,709
My Lord, you have my utmost loyalty.

47
00:03:51,710 --> 00:03:53,610
I dare not deceive you.

48
00:03:55,820 --> 00:03:57,870
Is there only loyalty?

49
00:03:58,750 --> 00:04:05,150
I remember that you adore me.

50
00:04:08,060 --> 00:04:12,030
Well... Indeed. I adore you.

51
00:04:12,030 --> 00:04:15,940
But there are many kinds of adoration.

52
00:04:17,910 --> 00:04:19,610
Which one is yours?

53
00:04:25,300 --> 00:04:29,290
Obviously, the kind with undying loyalty.

54
00:04:30,470 --> 00:04:32,780
"Undying loyalty"?

55
00:04:32,780 --> 00:04:40,140
Then if I get married one day, wouldn't you be heartbroken?

56
00:04:41,370 --> 00:04:42,870
My Lord,

57
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:44,750
has your illness been cured?

58
00:04:45,660 --> 00:04:47,360
What illness?

59
00:04:49,710 --> 00:04:51,940
It's nothing.

60
00:04:52,470 --> 00:04:58,440
My Lord, as long as you are happy, my feelings don't matter.

61
00:04:58,980 --> 00:05:03,050
Hurry to the study if you are done eating.

62
00:05:03,050 --> 00:05:05,730
I barely took a few bites.

63
00:05:09,030 --> 00:05:10,630
Thank you, My Lord.

64
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:14,190
Aren't you having any?

65
00:05:26,420 --> 00:05:28,290
Young Lady, what are you thinking about?

66
00:05:28,290 --> 00:05:29,990
You seem out of it.

67
00:05:31,530 --> 00:05:33,029
Juli,

68
00:05:33,030 --> 00:05:37,170
I think His Lordship was acting a little strange today.

69
00:05:37,170 --> 00:05:38,750
What happened?

70
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:42,120
He seemed preoccupied.

71
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:48,400
Was he trying to hint that I should treat his illness?

72
00:05:48,980 --> 00:05:50,469
That could be the reason.

73
00:05:50,470 --> 00:05:54,070
I guess men are usually too embarrassed to say such things.

74
00:05:56,740 --> 00:06:03,290
After this hectic period, I am going to find ways to treat this illness.

75
00:06:21,950 --> 00:06:23,149
Greetings, Your Highness.

76
00:06:23,150 --> 00:06:24,750
You're here.

77
00:06:25,220 --> 00:06:28,000
Playing pitch-pot, Your Highness?

78
00:06:28,510 --> 00:06:29,910
Yes.

79
00:06:29,910 --> 00:06:32,370
Sadly, I am not very good at it.

80
00:06:36,660 --> 00:06:38,659
I remember you are good at archery.

81
00:06:38,660 --> 00:06:42,360
How about giving it a shot so that I get to learn from you?

82
00:06:43,860 --> 00:06:46,460
I shall make a humble attempt, then.

83
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:12,470
As expected, you're great.

84
00:07:12,470 --> 00:07:15,659
I come from a family of hunters.

85
00:07:15,660 --> 00:07:19,540
I learned a few tricks since my father taught me when I was young.

86
00:07:19,540 --> 00:07:22,880
Your words just put many generals to shame.

87
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:24,680
I'm flattered.

88
00:07:26,390 --> 00:07:28,949
You don't have to teach the children today.

89
00:07:28,950 --> 00:07:31,980
Is there something important for your sudden visit?

90
00:07:32,660 --> 00:07:35,149
I actually came to ask for a leave of absence.

91
00:07:35,150 --> 00:07:37,659
The Northern Liang diplomatic corps will visit soon.

92
00:07:37,660 --> 00:07:41,339
Thanks to First Prince, I have joined the reception team.

93
00:07:41,340 --> 00:07:44,140
But the children's classes must not be held up.

94
00:07:44,140 --> 00:07:47,950
So I was hoping that you could find a substitute tutor.

95
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:50,339
That's a good thing for the nation and the people.

96
00:07:50,340 --> 00:07:52,850
Chen'er truly thinks highly of you.

97
00:07:53,420 --> 00:07:54,899
Feel free to do your duty.

98
00:07:54,900 --> 00:07:57,900
I will make arrangements for the children's classes.

99
00:08:02,100 --> 00:08:07,319
What are your thoughts on the Northern Liang diplomatic corps' sudden visit?

100
00:08:09,100 --> 00:08:10,640
It's not a friendly visit.

101
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:12,580
There's a hidden agenda.

102
00:08:34,460 --> 00:08:39,039
My Lord, there aren't many mistakes in this time's dictation. Right?

103
00:08:40,660 --> 00:08:42,260
You have a good memory.

104
00:08:42,260 --> 00:08:44,160
Only one word is wrong.

105
00:08:44,160 --> 00:08:46,979
That's for sure. After all, I work for you.

106
00:08:46,979 --> 00:08:50,010
I must be skilled in something.

107
00:08:53,870 --> 00:08:55,940
You've passed the test.

108
00:08:57,420 --> 00:08:59,120
Thank you, My Lord.

109
00:09:04,580 --> 00:09:06,749
We waited from dawn until noon.

110
00:09:06,750 --> 00:09:08,659
What is the Northern Liang diplomatic corps up to?

111
00:09:08,660 --> 00:09:09,749
Exactly.

112
00:09:09,750 --> 00:09:14,120
I have hosted a reception many times but never waited so long before.

113
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,870
Observer Mu.

114
00:09:15,870 --> 00:09:17,109
Brother Shen.

115
00:09:17,110 --> 00:09:18,269
It is so scorching today.

116
00:09:18,270 --> 00:09:19,659
You are so delicate as a woman.

117
00:09:19,660 --> 00:09:22,220
Why don't you take a rest under the pergola?

118
00:09:22,220 --> 00:09:25,140
Everyone is standing here, so I should too.

119
00:09:25,140 --> 00:09:29,929
Moreover, welcoming the Northern Liang diplomatic corps concerns our nation's prestige.

120
00:09:29,929 --> 00:09:32,170
I dare not be lax.

121
00:09:32,660 --> 00:09:34,229
You make a good point.

122
00:09:34,230 --> 00:09:37,269
Looks like I was being narrow-minded.

123
00:09:37,270 --> 00:09:40,819
Absolutely not. You were just concerned about me.

124
00:09:41,540 --> 00:09:45,730
 Report! Northern Liang emissaries have arrived! 

125
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:55,160
   

126
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:09,880
   

127
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:14,580
   

128
00:10:28,610 --> 00:10:31,060
   

129
00:10:31,820 --> 00:10:34,440
Welcome, Your Highness.

130
00:10:36,540 --> 00:10:38,509
It must have been a tiring journey.

131
00:10:38,510 --> 00:10:43,579
    
 His Majesty has prepared a feast in the palace to welcome your arrival.

132
00:10:43,579 --> 00:10:46,480
Please come with us to enter the capital.

133
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:49,520
I wish to do so.

134
00:10:49,520 --> 00:10:51,839
But the gate is too small.

135
00:10:51,839 --> 00:10:55,560
My imperial tents won't fit through.

136
00:11:04,540 --> 00:11:07,220
There is even a woman?

137
00:11:11,540 --> 00:11:14,579
I am Mu Zhuohua, the political observer of the Ministry of Rites.

138
00:11:14,580 --> 00:11:17,160
I am also a member of the reception team.

139
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:19,560
Greetings, Your Highness.

140
00:11:19,560 --> 00:11:23,640
Are the men in Southern Chen that incompetent?

141
00:11:24,180 --> 00:11:27,370
I can't believe you let a woman be an official.

142
00:11:31,700 --> 00:11:34,960
I am Shen Jinghong, the administrator of the Ministry of Revenue.

143
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:39,120
Since you come from afar, you must be unfamiliar with my nation.

144
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:42,649
His Majesty's political and military achievements benefit the whole nation.

145
00:11:42,649 --> 00:11:45,059
For men and women alike.

146
00:11:45,060 --> 00:11:48,880
Therefore, belittling women is out of the question,

147
00:11:48,880 --> 00:11:51,869
let alone treating women as slaves.

148
00:11:51,870 --> 00:11:56,190
So it is not uncommon for women to be an official in our imperial court.

149
00:11:56,190 --> 00:11:57,129
 Precisely. 

150
00:11:57,129 --> 00:12:00,380
Men and women are equal in Southern Chen.

151
00:12:04,350 --> 00:12:09,509
Your Highness, you don't know about Southern Chen just as we don't know about Northern Liang.

152
00:12:09,509 --> 00:12:11,509
Here in Southern Chen, we are a peaceful nation.

153
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:14,140
There is no burglary or theft.

154
00:12:14,750 --> 00:12:20,310
It is my first time seeing people bringing along their houses while traveling.

155
00:12:20,310 --> 00:12:22,310
It's not like we are snails.

156
00:12:22,780 --> 00:12:24,480
 How dare you! 

157
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:27,620
 How dare a lowly official not show any respect? 

158
00:12:27,620 --> 00:12:30,670
 Is this how Southern Chen respects someone superior? 

159
00:12:32,630 --> 00:12:35,080
Respect comes from the heart.

160
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:39,829
The most superior people would not feel disrespected even if they dine and sleep in the open.

161
00:12:39,829 --> 00:12:44,630
But those who are inferior would not appear noble even if His Majesty...

162
00:12:45,230 --> 00:12:46,939
welcomes them personally.

163
00:12:46,940 --> 00:12:48,840
Watch your tongue.

164
00:13:02,630 --> 00:13:04,480
Mu Zhuohua.

165
00:13:05,420 --> 00:13:07,670
You impressed me.

166
00:13:09,540 --> 00:13:11,580
It would be my honor.

167
00:13:12,060 --> 00:13:13,990
This way, Your Highness.

168
00:13:14,810 --> 00:13:18,870
   

169
00:13:22,110 --> 00:13:24,880
How dare a lowly official

170
00:13:24,880 --> 00:13:28,160
humiliate me in public like that

171
00:13:28,160 --> 00:13:31,290
by using my background against me?

172
00:13:31,290 --> 00:13:33,550
How dare she!

173
00:13:36,660 --> 00:13:39,799
 Your Highness, a eunuch is here with a decree. 

174
00:13:55,010 --> 00:13:57,250
   

175
00:14:03,350 --> 00:14:06,919
Your Highness, please bow to accept the imperial decree.

176
00:14:17,630 --> 00:14:23,629
"Prince Yemu, since you have traveled a long and arduous journey to make it here,

177
00:14:23,629 --> 00:14:28,389
I have specially prepared a banquet in the palace to welcome the emissaries.

178
00:14:28,389 --> 00:14:31,269
I grant you my permission."

179
00:14:31,270 --> 00:14:33,150
Thank you, Your Majesty.

180
00:14:33,630 --> 00:14:34,819
Your Highness,

181
00:14:34,820 --> 00:14:38,269
by the law of Southern Chen, weapons are forbidden during an audience with His Majesty.

182
00:14:38,269 --> 00:14:41,220
I would like to ask for your cooperation.

183
00:15:23,460 --> 00:15:25,060
What's the matter?

184
00:15:27,580 --> 00:15:32,250
Is there something wrong with the hand of my mute slave?

185
00:16:13,420 --> 00:16:14,920
I am Yemu Jing from Northern Liang.

186
00:16:14,920 --> 00:16:17,120
Greetings, Your Majesty.

187
00:16:18,150 --> 00:16:19,750
At ease.

188
00:16:22,180 --> 00:16:24,659
It must have been an arduous journey to come here.

189
00:16:24,660 --> 00:16:26,109
Thank you for your concern, Your Majesty.

190
00:16:26,110 --> 00:16:28,879
Master Huiming was a highly virtuous senior monk of Northern Liang.

191
00:16:28,879 --> 00:16:32,629
It is our honor to present this Sarira to Your Majesty.

192
00:16:32,630 --> 00:16:34,330
I dare not complain.

193
00:16:38,300 --> 00:16:43,580
Southern Chen is truly lucky to receive this treasure.

194
00:16:54,460 --> 00:16:55,960
Take a seat.

195
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:57,930
Thank you, Your Majesty.

196
00:17:05,350 --> 00:17:10,149
Prince Yemu, welcome to my nation.

197
00:17:51,390 --> 00:17:53,270
You've got quite the nerve.

198
00:17:53,270 --> 00:17:59,160
Do you think it was your place as a low-ranking observer to speak at the city gate earlier today?

199
00:17:59,160 --> 00:18:02,329
My Lord, subjects must defend their ruler.

200
00:18:02,350 --> 00:18:04,349
He insulted the people of Southern Chen.

201
00:18:04,350 --> 00:18:07,520
I spoke up to defend my nation and showed patriotism.

202
00:18:07,550 --> 00:18:11,010
You should be praising me, My Lord.

203
00:18:12,630 --> 00:18:16,360
Yemu Jing is atrocious.

204
00:18:16,360 --> 00:18:18,620
Aren't you afraid of offending him?

205
00:18:18,620 --> 00:18:20,869
He is in the lands of Southern Chen.

206
00:18:20,870 --> 00:18:22,710
What can he do to me?

207
00:18:23,310 --> 00:18:27,449
Furthermore, I have you to protect me.

208
00:18:27,449 --> 00:18:28,950
Am I right?

209
00:18:29,630 --> 00:18:31,629
Then you must stay close to me.

210
00:18:31,630 --> 00:18:35,530
Don't fall behind in case he wants revenge.

211
00:18:35,530 --> 00:18:37,030
Understood, My Lord.

212
00:18:59,150 --> 00:19:01,050
Your Majesty.

213
00:19:01,050 --> 00:19:05,019
To show our intentions to form a lasting friendly relationship with Southern Chen,

214
00:19:05,019 --> 00:19:08,490
I have specially prepared a valuable gift.

215
00:19:30,020 --> 00:19:31,520
Your Majesty,

216
00:19:31,520 --> 00:19:33,739
this is my younger sister, Yemu Zhen.

217
00:19:33,740 --> 00:19:38,320
She is 20 years old and the most beautiful woman in Northern Liang.

218
00:19:45,530 --> 00:19:50,810
   

219
00:19:59,740 --> 00:20:01,670
A honey trap.

220
00:20:03,260 --> 00:20:04,830
What a disgrace.

221
00:20:05,390 --> 00:20:06,990
Chen'er.

222
00:20:14,020 --> 00:20:15,720
Your Majesty,

223
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:17,979
this is a sincere gift from Northern Liang.

224
00:20:17,980 --> 00:20:22,120
I hope you will accept it and treat my sister well.

225
00:20:28,630 --> 00:20:30,920
I appreciate the thought.

226
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:33,019
It's just that Princess Yemu is still so young.

227
00:20:33,020 --> 00:20:37,850
I feel sorry that she has to be so far away from home.

228
00:20:38,550 --> 00:20:41,490
Here's the thing, Your Majesty.

229
00:20:42,020 --> 00:20:45,750
Northern Liang will never take back a gift.

230
00:20:45,750 --> 00:20:50,230
Otherwise, we would deem it as disrespect.

231
00:20:58,220 --> 00:21:01,419
If you are afraid of mistreating my sister,

232
00:21:01,420 --> 00:21:05,749
you can betroth her to an imperial family member who is of marriageable age.

233
00:21:06,740 --> 00:21:11,760
I heard that Lord Ding is still not married.

234
00:21:18,180 --> 00:21:22,339
 This cunning fox of Northern Liang is truly disgusting. 

235
00:21:30,830 --> 00:21:37,749
I did not expect such a huge difference between the customs of Northern Liang and Southern Chen.

236
00:21:38,550 --> 00:21:42,730
I can't believe you would present a woman as a gift.

237
00:21:42,730 --> 00:21:45,950
Since this is a sincere gift from Northern Liang,

238
00:21:45,950 --> 00:21:49,300
it would be rude of us to decline.

239
00:21:49,300 --> 00:21:51,480
We will definitely treat her well.

240
00:21:57,660 --> 00:21:59,260
Your Majesty,

241
00:21:59,260 --> 00:22:03,260
I would like to ask you to take Yemu Zhen in as your goddaughter.

242
00:22:04,390 --> 00:22:06,390
Lord Ding.

243
00:22:09,120 --> 00:22:11,290
That is a good idea.

244
00:22:13,220 --> 00:22:16,920
Princess Yemu is a princess in Northern Liang.

245
00:22:16,920 --> 00:22:20,020
She will still be a princess here in Southern Chen.

246
00:22:20,020 --> 00:22:22,350
She will not be mistreated.

247
00:22:22,350 --> 00:22:26,730
His Majesty and the empress will also get her a good teacher

248
00:22:26,730 --> 00:22:31,620
to teach her the etiquette and culture of Southern Chen to refine her overall qualities.

249
00:22:31,620 --> 00:22:36,269
That will also do justice to her title as the most beautiful woman in the world.

250
00:22:40,500 --> 00:22:42,200
Father.

251
00:22:42,200 --> 00:22:44,580
I think Princess Yemu and I will get along.

252
00:22:44,580 --> 00:22:47,389
How about letting her stay with me?

253
00:22:47,390 --> 00:22:49,829
Not only can I take care of her daily necessities,

254
00:22:49,830 --> 00:22:52,969
but I can also show her around the capital.

255
00:22:52,969 --> 00:22:56,259
Good. I approve.

256
00:23:00,310 --> 00:23:04,900
In that case, I shall thank you, Your Majesty.

257
00:23:06,220 --> 00:23:08,100
Lord Ding,

258
00:23:08,100 --> 00:23:10,419
you and I are considered old acquaintances.

259
00:23:10,420 --> 00:23:13,499
I brought lots of good wine from Northern Liang with me.

260
00:23:13,500 --> 00:23:15,950
I would like to catch up with you.

261
00:23:15,950 --> 00:23:20,800
