262
00:23:20,800 --> 00:23:22,840
You are my guest.

263
00:23:22,840 --> 00:23:25,190
I should be the host.

264
00:23:26,150 --> 00:23:29,150
Northern Liang is good at martial arts and hunting.

265
00:23:29,150 --> 00:23:34,550
